The '''Caucasian snow vole''' (''Chionomys gud'') is a species of [[rodent]] in the family [[Cricetidae]].

It is found in [[Georgia (country)|Georgia]], [[Russian Federation]], and [[Turkey]].

Its natural [[habitat]]s are temperate [[forest]]s and temperate [[grassland]].

